          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20052,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005201,
            "DisplayOrder": 620,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8100,
            "LocalizeKR": "다 되었나요?\n그러면 이제,\n선생님도 하시죠.",
            "LocalizeJP": "撮れました？\nでは次は先生の番です。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20052,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005201,
            "DisplayOrder": 630,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13700,
            "LocalizeKR": "어라, 이거 저에게만\n시킬 생각이셨나요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "あれ？\n……まさか私にだけ\nやらせるつもりですかぁ？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20052,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005201,
            "DisplayOrder": 640,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 14500,
            "LocalizeKR": "저런, 저런. 그건\n너무 안일하다고\n생각하는데요, 선생님?",
            "LocalizeJP": "やれやれ、それは\nあまりにも安易だと\n思いますけどねぇ？先生？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
